text: Marjolein Buis and Diede de Groot were the defending champions, but chose to compete with different partners. De Groot successfully defended her title alongside Yui Kamiji, defeating Buis and Aniek van Koot in the final, 6–3, 6–4. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Bracket=== == External links == * Draw Wheelchair Women's Doubles U.S. Open, 2018 Women's Doubles
